<html>
  <body>
    <h2 style="color: #333">Dear <%= name %>,</h2>

    <p>
      We are pleased to inform you that we have accepted your donation request. Your support is invaluable to us, and we deeply appreciate your commitment to our cause.
    </p>

    <% if (donationItems && donationItems.length > 0) { %>
      <p>Your donation details are as follows:</p>
      <ul>
        <% donationItems.forEach(function(item) { %>
          <li>
            <strong>Item:</strong> <%= item.ItemName %> - 
            <strong>Quantity:</strong> <%= item.quantity %> <%= item.quantity === 1 ? 'item' : 'items' %>
          </li>
        <% }); %>
      </ul>
    <% } else { %>
      <p>It seems there was an error processing your donation details. Please contact us to resolve this issue.</p>
    <% } %>

    <p>
      Please hand over your donation at your earliest convenience. You can deliver your donation to our facility at the following address:
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Apeksha Hospital Maharagama</strong><br>
      [Insert Hospital Address Here]
    </p>

    <p>
      If you have any questions or need further assistance, please do not hesitate to reach out to our support team at
      <a href="mailto:donation@apekshahospital.com">donation@apekshahospital.com</a>.
    </p>

    <p>Once again, thank you for your generosity and support.</p>

    <p>Warm regards,</p>
    <p>Apeksha Hospital Maharagama</p>
  </body>
</html>
